OL,3,CBehind locked doors at psychiatric
OL,4,Chospital, as services struggle to cope
OL,6,FITV News Health Correspondent Rebecca
OL,7,FBarry goes to Oxleas House, a secure
OL,8,Fpsychiatric hospital as struggling
OL,9,Ffacilities in the UK reach breaking
OL,10,Fpoint
OL,12,FWe've been given rare access to film
OL,13,Fwhat goes on behind the locked doors
OL,14,Fof a psychiatric hospital.
OL,16,FWe're at Oxleas House in South London,
OL,17,Fwhere people are treated when their
OL,18,Fmental health reaches crisis point.
