OL,3,CBehind locked doors at psychiatric
OL,4,Chospital, as services struggle to cope
OL,6,FFifteen out of the 20 women on the
OL,7,Fward we visited had been sectioned;
OL,8,Fthat means they've been detained for
OL,9,Ftheir safety or the protection of
OL,10,Fothers.
OL,12,FSome of the patients have depression,
OL,13,Fand others are being treated for
OL,14,Fanxiety disorders or schizophrenia.
OL,16,FWe watch as the women play games, get
OL,17,Fmedical checks and receive medication.
