OL,3,CBehind locked doors at psychiatric
OL,4,Chospital, as services struggle to cope
OL,6,FBut across England, mental health
OL,7,Fservices are creaking, leaving
OL,8,Fthousands to descend into mental
OL,9,Fhealth emergencies.
OL,11,FWant a quick and expert briefing on
OL,12,Fthe biggest news stories? Listen to
OL,13,Four latest podcasts to find out What
OL,14,FYou Need To Know...
OL,16,FNewly-published data from NHS England
OL,17,Ftells us 51,312 people were sectioned
OL,18,Funder the Mental Health Act last year.
