OL,3,CBehind locked doors at psychiatric
OL,4,Chospital, as services struggle to cope
OL,6,FBlack people are nearly four times
OL,7,Fmore likely to be detained under the
OL,8,FMental Health Act than white people.
OL,10,FAs are people from deprived areas.
OL,12,FAnd there has been a 53% increase in
OL,13,Fthe number of children in a mental
OL,14,Fhealth crisis since 2019.
OL,16,FConsultant Psychiatrist, Dr Emma
OL,17,FPadfield, says more should be done
OL,18,Fsooner.
