OL,3,CBehind locked doors at psychiatric
OL,4,Chospital, as services struggle to cope
OL,6,F"I think there are failures in the
OL,7,Fsystem in general," Dr Padfield tells
OL,8,Fme.
OL,10,FShe says that resources aren't in
OL,11,Fplace to provide the care which is
OL,12,Fneeded to prevent patients from
OL,13,Freaching a point of crisis.
OL,15,FThe latest inspection of her site -
OL,16,Fpart of Oxleas NHS Foundation Trust -
OL,17,Ffound patients are treated with
OL,18,Frespect, and given therapy and
OL,19,Frehabilitation.
