OL,3,CBehind locked doors at psychiatric
OL,4,Chospital, as services struggle to cope
OL,6,FBut elsewhere, some feel more harmed
OL,7,Fthan healed by the system.
OL,9,FI met Tiwa, who was sectioned under
OL,10,Fthe Mental Health Act between the ages
OL,11,Fof 16 and 18.
OL,13,FShe showed me photos of herself while
OL,14,Fshe was in hospital.
OL,16,F"This is where I'd self-harmed and was
OL,17,Fby myself for hours. I almost don't
OL,18,Frecognise her - she was so desperate
OL,19,Fand so sad," Tiwa tells me.
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@LO]
