OL,3,CBehind locked doors at psychiatric
OL,4,Chospital, as services struggle to cope
OL,6,FShe feels the experience in the
OL,7,Fhospital only added to her trauma.
OL,9,F"It was such a difficult environment
OL,10,Fand often I felt quite alone. I didn't
OL,11,Freally have much say in anything,"
OL,12,FTiwa says.
OL,14,FTiwa started to self-harm as a
OL,15,Fteenager and feels if she'd had the
OL,16,Fright therapy sooner, she wouldn't
OL,17,Fhave been sectioned.
