OL,6,F"The waiting lists for therapy are so
OL,7,Flong and your mental health doesn't
OL,8,Fpause whilst you're waiting for
OL,9,Fanything - all that's going to happen
OL,10,Fis it's going to get worse," Tiwa says.
OL,12,FTiwa's mental health is now much
OL,13,Fbetter and she's studying for a
OL,14,Fdegree. She hopes that by speaking
OL,15,Fout, she can help improve the system
OL,16,Ffor others.
OL,18,FBut Tiwa's story is - sadly - not
OL,19,Funique.
