OL,3,CBehind locked doors at psychiatric
OL,4,Chospital, as services struggle to cope
OL,6,FDr Lade Smith, President of the Royal
OL,7,FCollege of Psychiatrists, tells me
OL,8,Fthat services are "overstretched" and
OL,9,F"chronically under-resourced."
OL,11,FShe says deprivation and
OL,12,Fdiscrimination increase the risk of
OL,13,Fsomeone developing a mental health
OL,14,Fproblem.
OL,16,FAsked if we should feel ashamed of the
OL,17,Fstate of our country's mental health
OL,18,Fservice, Dr Smith tells me "yes, we
OL,19,Freally should. They're just not good
OL,20,Fenough."
