OL,6,FAn NHS spokesperson said: "While the
OL,7,Fpandemic inevitably had an impact on
OL,8,Fthe nation's mental health causing an
OL,9,Fincrease in demand across the board,
OL,10,Fthe NHS is focused on ensuring people
OL,11,Fare given appropriate support close to
OL,12,Fhome in the community before an
OL,13,Fadmission to hospital is needed -
OL,14,Ffunding has increased by #1 billion a
OL,15,Fyear to transform community mental
OL,16,Fhealth services to meet demand.
